            "text": " The results in Fig.  $3$  are an advancement on work that showed that sub-barrier fusion is enhanced when channel couplings are included, due to the fusion contribution of excited states  $[29]$ . The thermal increase in fusion probability can be explained by studying the radial wave function of the entrance channel,",
